comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-31T22:18:36.254Z",maintainer-agent,"Unblocked + ready: pm-kfd8 (closed this PR) shipped assertRegisteredSearchProvider in src/sdk/testing.ts (matches on definition.name over registrations.search_providers). When this item teaches pm-search-advanced to api.registerSearchProvider(...), its package spec should assert via assertRegisteredSearchProvider for a non-synthetic first-party exemplar. Finding: pm-search-advanced currently only registers commands+flags, not a SearchProvider — this item is the real search-capability exemplar."
